::DarkMouse::

She gave a small smile to Scorponok.
"Well, it's 98% finished commander.  I have finished the escape tunnel and 
got the computer systems running.  I also got the auto-defence systems up 
and running.  I just need your help with the scanners and a few other little 
things is all commander.  I got the internal scanners up and I fixed the 
main console so you and the other commanders can run the whole base from 
there.  It will only respond to your voice commands so no one else other 
than us four  can run it."
She thought for a moment that she was over stepping her bounds.
"Uh, but I can remove my voice command capability from it if you wish 
commander."
